Business Demand Overview

Reporter: Steven - Sales Manager
Value of Change: Visual Dashboards and improved Sales reporting or follow up for salesforce
Necessary Systems: Power BI, CRM System
Other Relevant Info: Budgets have been delivered in excel for 2023

User Stories:

No #:
As a [role]:
I want {request/demand}:
So that I {user value}:
Acceptance Criteria:

1
Sales Manager
To get a dashboard overview of internet sales
Can follow better with customers and products with the best
A Power BI dashboard that updates data once a day

2
Sales Representative
A detailed overview of internet sales per customers
Can follow up on my customers that buy the most and who we can sell one too
A Power BI dashboard that allows me to filter data per customer

3
Sales Representative
A detailed overview of internet sales per products
Can follow up on my products that sell the most
A Power BI dashboard that allows me to filter data per product

4
Sales Manager
A dashboard overview of internet sales
Follow sales over time against budget
A Power Bi dashboard with graphs and KPIs comparing against budget



